\c 11
\s Ukuxwayisa ngenhlupheko yetshumi: Ukufa kwamazibulo
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Ngisezakwehlisela kuFaro lakulo iGibhithe inhlupheko eyodwa\x + 4.23.\x*; emva kwalokho uzaliyekela lihambe lisuke lapha; ekuliyekeleni kwakhe lihambe uzalixotsha lokulixotsha lisuka lapha ngokupheleleyo\x + 12.31,33,39.\x*.
\v 2 Ake ukhulume endlebeni zabantu, ukuthi bacele, ngulowo kumakhelwane wakhe, lalowo owesifazana kumakhelwane wakhe, izinto zesiliva lezinto zegolide\x + 3.22; 12.35.\x*.
\v 3 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasinika abantu umusa emehlweni amaGibhithe\x + 3.22; 12.35.\x*. Futhi indoda uMozisi waba mkhulu kakhulu elizweni leGibhithe emehlweni enceku zikaFaro lemehlweni esizwe.
\p
\v 4 UMozisi wasesithi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* \add ithi\add*: Phose phakathi kobusuku ngizaphuma ngiye phakathi kweGibhithe\x + 12.29. Amos 4.10.\x*;
\v 5 lawo wonke amazibulo elizweni leGibhithe azakufa, kusukela kuzibulo likaFaro elizahlala esihlalweni sakhe sobukhosi, kuze kube kuzibulo lencekukazi engemva kwelitshe lokuchola, lamazibulo wonke ezifuyo\x + Hlu. 16.21. Mat. 24.41.\x*.
\v 6 Njalo kuzakuba khona isililo esikhulu elizweni lonke leGibhithe, esingazanga sibe khona esinjengaso, lesingayikuba khona futhi esinjengaso\x + 12.30. Amos 5.16,17.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa lakubo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli inja kayiyikunyikinya ulimi lwayo\x + Josh. 10.21.\x*, kusukela emuntwini kusiya ezifuyweni, ukuze lazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* iyehlukanisa phakathi kweGibhithe loIsrayeli\x + 8.22; 9.4.\x*.
\v 8 Lazo zonke izinceku zakho lezi zizakwehlela kimi, zingikhothamele zisithi: Phuma wena lesizwe sonke esikulandelayo. Langemva kwalokho ngizaphuma\x + 12.33.\x*. Wasephuma kuFaro ekuvutheni kolaka.
\p
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: UFaro kayikulizwa\x + 3.19; 7.4; 10.1.\x*, ukuze zande izimangaliso zami elizweni leGibhithe\x + 7.3.\x*.
\v 10 OMozisi loAroni basebesenza zonke lezizimangaliso phambi kukaFaro, kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yenza inhliziyo kaFaro yaba lukhuni, kazabayekela abantwana bakoIsrayeli baphume elizweni lakhe\x + 10.20.\x*.
